snippet.title: Rockman 8 Famicom Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www31.atwiki.jp/rockman8/
http://demake.web.fc2.com/

This is a fanmade trailer for the project Rockman 8FC, an 8-bit "demake" of the playstation original by Capcom, featuring Famicom (NES) versions of all the stages, bosses, graphics and music.
The game is still in its beta stages but is now fully playable from start to finish.

Rock Man belongs to Capcom, this is a fan made trailer of a fan made game.
